'''Champion'''是[[美国|美国]]一家服装制造商，以生產和銷售运动服装為特色。该公司是{{link-en|汉佰公司|Hanesbrands}}的子公司<ref name="tribune">{{Cite news|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1989-02-14-8903050345-story.html|title=Sara Lee Adds Champion Sportswear To Wardrobe|author=Key|first=Janet|date=14 February 1989|work=Chicago Tribune|accessdate=17 Jan 2020|archive-date=2020-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321001013/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1989-02-14-8903050345-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Champion由芬布鲁姆（Feinbloom）兄弟<ref>{{Cite web|title=The History of Champion|url=https://theidleman.com/manual/arrivals/brands/the-history-of-champion/|accessdate=17 Jan 2020|author=|date=13 November 2018|first=|work=The Idle Man|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905002626/https://www.theidleman.com/manual/arrivals/brands/the-history-of-champion/|archivedate=2020-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>于1919年創辦，當時名为 “尼克博克针织公司”（Knickerbocker Knitting Company）。20世纪30年代，公司更名为“Champion Knitting Mills Inc.”<ref name="champeu">[http://www.champion-eu.com/about-us About us] {{Wayback|url=http://www.champion-eu.com/about-us |date=20200725144753 }} on Champion-eu website</ref>。  

